I"u<p><a class="internal-link" href="/about">My</a> second brain is a large collection of plain text files that I maintain as a repository for things I would like to retrieve later but don’t want to remember now. The public part of it can be found on this website, my <a href="/digital-garden">digital garden</a>.</p>

<h3 id="tools">Tools</h3>
<p>It’s important for me to remember <a class="internal-link" href="/tools-don-t-matter">Tools don’t matter</a>. The only thing that matters about a tool is that it must allow me to manipulate plain text or Markdown files that exist in a folder that I can move around freely.</p>

